// Reconstructed for OpenRide T3/#3 — interoperability with the Peloton Bike Gen 2 tablet's
// on-device affernet system service (com.onepeloton.affernetservice). This declares the
// existing Parcelable so the AIDL toolchain can reference it; the wire layout is implemented
// in com.onepeloton.affernetservice.BikeData (Kotlin), reverse-engineered from the observed
// Parcel format. See docs/SENSOR_PROTOCOL.md.
package com.onepeloton.affernetservice;

parcelable BikeData;
